## Project Overview
Production-ready Jmix application template demonstrating **Vibe Coding** philosophy: strict quality gates, minimal suppressions, senior-level code standards.

## Tech Stack
- **Java 21** (virtual threads, pattern matching, records)
- **Jmix 2.7.1** | **Vaadin FlowUI 24+** | **Spring Boot 3.x**
- **PostgreSQL 16** | **Liquibase** | **EclipseLink**
- **Quality**: Palantir Baseline (Checkstyle, PMD, SpotBugs, Spotless, Error-prone), SonarLint

## Core Principles
- **Production-ready code** from day one
- **Senior+ level** standards
- **Minimal suppressions, maximum quality** (vibe coding)
- **Fix root causes, not symptoms**
- **Refactor, not workarounds**

## Quick Commands
- `make analyze-full` - Check quality (Checkstyle, PMD, SpotBugs, SonarLint)
- `make test` - Run tests
- `make format` - Format code
- `make setup` - Setup project

## Quality Gates
- **Coverage**: 85% instructions, 75% branches, 90% lines
- **Complexity**: ≤10 cognitive/cyclomatic per method
- **File Length**: ≤250 lines
- **All checks**: Must pass (`ignoreFailures=false`)

